{
  "texts": [
    "Goldman Sachs (2023) estimates that GenAI alone could raise annual US labor-productivity growth by just under 1.5 percentage points, following widespread adoption.",
    "In a controlled experiment, software developers who used GitHub Copilot GenAI completed their task (implementing an HTTP server in JavaScript) 55.8% faster than those who did not have access to GitHub Copilot (Peng et al, 2023).",
    "In another experiment, participants (college-educated professionals) who used GenAI (ChatGPT, in this case) to complete a writing task were 40% more productive than participants who did not use GenAI.",
    "Furthermore, the quality of output of those who used ChatGPT rose by 18% (Noy & Zhang, 2023).",
    "While GenAI has the potential to significantly enhance productivity, realizing these benefits hinges on employees' willingness to effectively leverage these tools."
  ]
}